<note n="0106006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106006">原本冠註曰此大真言王分句與經少異而詳其義今軌得宜</note>
<note n="0107001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107001">原本冠註曰一本無一馱羅野經及攝軌同之疏及玄青二軌同今</note>
<note n="0107002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107002">原本冠註曰為一經及攝青二軌皆作為二</note>
<note n="0107003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107003">原本冠註曰一一經及攝青兩軌並作第一</note>
